text:
I don't usually wear this kind of thing at all...
besides, Isn't it a bit... too flashy for me?

It'll be fine!
Just try it on for once!

...Alright, I'll give it a try.
After all, it's the coordinated outfit you two chose for me.

Yeah... it's different from usual, Chiyuki-san...
Really lovely...

Hey!
Feels like a new Chiyuki-san...!

A new me... yeah.
Sometimes you don't know until you dive in, right...?
Then let's... go ahead and buy it!
